International Monetary Fund Endorses Burundi’s Revised Economic Program

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-07-19T21:20:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/international-monetary-fund-endorses-burundi-s-revised-economic-program.html
The International Monetary Fund said
its executive board agreed that  Burundi ’s revised program for
2011 “strikes the appropriate balance” between keeping the
economy stable and cushioning higher prices for food and energy.
The fund commented in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
